@59   = ~I already know the rest, I think.~
@60   = ~Let me briefly outline the most important parts, <CHARNAME>. I wrote you letters, which I then stored at the Order since they could not reach you... I did not meet my parents in Waterdeep, as we had agreed upon. I was recalled by the Order, since the tensions on the Sword Coast and the threatening war with Amn made many missions for the Order necessary.~
